text: Roadhouse Nights is a 1930 American crime movie directed by Hobart Henley and starring Helen Morgan, Charles Ruggles, Fred Kohler, Jimmy Durante, Tammany Young, Lou Clayton. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1930 crime movies Category:American crime movies Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Hobart Henley
